Sentencas: The oxygen tracer diffusion coefficient, D*, and the oxygen tracer surface exchange coefficient, k*, were measured in La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta over the temperature range of 406-680 degrees C and the oxygen partial pressure range 0.044-1.019 bar.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ

Sentencas: Distortions of the near surface regions of the diffusion profiles were observed in several specimens.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ

Sentencas: O-18 exchange experiments were modeled by the Finite Element method and the origin of the observed distortions was assigned to exchange of oxygen during sample cooling.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ

Sentencas: The estimated error in the determination of D* and k* was found to be less than 20%.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ

Sentencas: The activation energies of D* and k* were 1.84 +/- 0.02 eV and 0.76 +/- 0.13 eV, respectively.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ

Sentencas: D* was found to decrease with oxygen partial pressure following the power law with a power of -0.55 +/- 0.10.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ

Sentencas: The effect of Sr doping on the values of D* in Ln(1-x)Sr(x)CoO(3-delta) (Ln = La, Sm) perovskites is discussed.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ

Sentencas: The data obtained from isotopic exchange measurements at 500-600 degrees C are in good agreement with the kinetic parameters derived from conductivity relaxation experiments on samples from the same batch.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ
